<p><strong>PRIVACY POLICY</strong><br />
<br />
This Privacy Policy applies to Sudoku : ScieNext.<br />
<br />
Our Services are designed to avoid collecting information such as your name, address, email address or other similar contact data unless you provide such data to us.&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong>Information we collect:</strong><br />
We do NOT collect any information if you download&nbsp;and play our&nbsp;Game.</p>

<p>We may collect non-personal identification, such as device-specific information, including your operating system version, system language. All of these are for serving you better.</p>

<p><strong>How we use information we collect:</strong><br />
Personal information - Since we do not collect Personal Information, we may not use your personal information in any way.</p>

<p>Non-Personal Information - We may use your Non-Personal Information to personalize user experience, or to help improve our products.</p>


<p><strong>Information security:</strong><br />
We are very concerned about safeguarding the confidentiality of your information. We do not collect Personal Information, and we employ administrative, physical and electronic measures designed to protect your Non-Personal Information from unauthorized access and use. Please be aware that no security measures that we take to protect your information is absolutely guaranteed to avoid unauthorized access or use of your Non-Personal Information which is impenetrable.</p>

<p><strong>Changes:</strong><br />
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Thus, you are advised to review this page periodically for any changes. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page and within the app. These changes are effective immediately after they are posted on this page.</p>

<p><strong>Contact us:</strong><br />
If you have questions or concerns about our privacy practices, please contact us via email at <a href="mailto:scienext@live.com">scienext@live.com</a></p>

